Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.43,0:01:39.73,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}宇宙的年龄和体积\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The age and size of the cosmos
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.76,0:01:42.87,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}由光来书写\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}are written in light.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.90,0:01:47.74,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}迷人的本质和恒星的物质\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The nature of beauty and the substance of the stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.77,0:01:51.14,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}时空的定律\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the laws of space and time...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.18,0:01:54.14,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原本就存在\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they were there all along,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.18,0:01:56.18,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我们过去未能发现\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but we never saw them...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.21,0:02:00.05,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}直到我们拥有了更为强大的观察方式\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}until we devised a more powerful way of seeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.08,0:02:03.75,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这种觉醒的故事有很多的开始\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The story of this awakening has many beginnings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.79,0:02:05.92,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}却不会终止\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and no ending.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.96,0:02:09.16,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从不同时间和地方涌现出许多的英雄\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Its heroes come from many times and places--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.19,0:02:12.00,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}中国古代的哲人\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}an Ancient Chinese philosopher,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.03,0:02:15.70,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}令11世纪伊拉克穆斯林统治者叹服的奇才\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a wizard who amazed the caliphs of 11th-century Iraq,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.73,0:02:20.60,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}被苛刻奴役的德国可怜孤儿\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a poor German orphan enslaved to a harsh master.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.64,0:02:23.07,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每一位都带领我们前进一小步\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Each one brought us a little closer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.11,0:02:27.31,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在解开光线之谜的道路上\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to unlocking the secrets hidden in light.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.95,0:02:33.38,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大多数的名字都已经被遗忘了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Most of their names are forever lost to us,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:37.92,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但在某处  很久前  某人的匆匆一瞥\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but somewhere, long ago, someone glanced up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.96,0:02:42.33,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}注意到了光线展示出的神奇\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to see light perform one of its magic tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.15,0:03:04.15,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谁知道呢\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.18,0:03:05.95,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或许光线的偶然作为\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Maybe that quirk of light
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.98,0:03:08.12,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为第一位艺术家带来了灵感\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}inspired the very first artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.36,0:03:23.40,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这些都是怎么来的\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Where did all this come from?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:27.00,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们是如何从小量聚居的\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}How did we evolve from small wandering bands
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:29.17,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}采集者和猎人 进化而来的\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of hunters and gatherers living beneath the stars
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.21,0:03:32.98,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最后还成为世界文明的缔造者\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to become the builders of a global civilization?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.01,0:03:36.45,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}中间的过程是怎样的\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}How did we get from there to here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:38.28,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有统一的答案\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}There's no one answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.32,0:03:40.98,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}气候的变化  学会控制火\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Climate change, the domestication of fire,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.02,0:03:45.52,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}工具的发明 语言发明 农业发展\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the invention of tools,  language, agriculture
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.56,0:03:48.83,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}都有各自的功劳\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}all played a role.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.86,0:03:51.49,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或许还有其它的\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Maybe there was something else, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.53,0:03:54.66,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}中国  2000多年前\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In China, more than 2,000 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.70,0:03:57.87,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一位名叫 墨子 的哲人 据说发现了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a philosopher named Mo Tze is said to have observed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.90,0:04:00.27,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}光线可以在密闭的宝库中\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that light could be made to paint a picture
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:02.54,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei UI\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}即小孔成像
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:02.54,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}产生图像\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}inside a locked treasure room.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.57,0:04:08.01,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这描述的就是第一台照相机\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This was the description of the first camera...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.05,0:04:10.15,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}暗箱\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the camera obscura,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.18,0:04:12.55,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所有成像照相机的原型\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the prototype of all image-forming cameras,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:15.85,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}包括给你带来图像的这台摄像机\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}including the one that's bringing you this picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.89,0:04:18.49,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}利用光线这种有趣的现象\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Taking advantage of this funny thing that light does
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.52,0:04:23.49,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}催生了首部的电影\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}resulted in what could be called the first movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:29.30,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}墨子 光线大师  专治各种黑暗\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mo Tze, master of light, worked against all forms of darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.33,0:04:31.07,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}军事天才\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A military genius
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:34.24,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以智抑暴\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}who only used his talents to prevent violence,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.27,0:04:36.24,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他最著名的成就是\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}he was legendary for traveling
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.27,0:04:38.38,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}穿行于战乱的国家间\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}among the kingdoms of the warring states,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.41,0:04:40.14,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}运用巧妙地策略\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}employing ingenious strategies
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.18,0:04:42.21,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}劝导各方休战\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to talk kings out of going to war.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.25,0:04:45.82,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他是兼爱的倡导者\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He was one of the first to dream of universal love
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.85,0:04:48.92,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}提倡消灭统治者带给人们的\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and an end to poverty and other forms of inequality;
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.95,0:04:52.89,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}贫困与不公\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of government for the people...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.92,0:04:56.76,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}批判对于宗教和权威的盲从\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and to argue against blind obedience to ritual and authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.79,0:04:58.36,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在他的著作中  你能发现\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In his writings, you can find
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.40,0:05:02.10,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}科学探索的早期萌芽\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}early stirrings of the scientific approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.13,0:05:05.07,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到墨子那个年代  中国人已经开始\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}By Mo Tze's time, the Chinese had already been recording
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.10,0:05:08.44,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}用书籍记录他们的思想 至少上千年了\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}their thoughts in books for at least a thousand years.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:11.41,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我们对他的了解 依然仅是只字词组\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Still, our knowledge of him is only fragmentary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.44,0:05:13.88,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}通过许多由他和他的追随者\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It consists largely of the collection of essays
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.91,0:05:15.58,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所著的文集而来\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}attributed to him and his disciples.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.61,0:05:18.75,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其中一篇 题为《非命》\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In one of them, entitled "Against Fate,"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.78,0:05:21.89,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei UI\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}故言必有三表
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.78,0:05:21.89,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}立论一定要有三项标准\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a three-pronged test for every doctrine is proposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:24.42,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}推究来历\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Question its basis--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:24.42,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei UI\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}一、有本之者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.46,0:05:25.24,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是否可以由\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ask if it can be verified
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.16,0:05:28.69,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei UI\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}二、有原之者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.40,0:05:28.20,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}普通人的观感再次验证的\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}...by the sights and senses of common people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.73,0:05:30.46,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是否可以推广\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ask how it is to be applied
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:32.83,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fnMicrosoft JhengHei UI\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}三、有用之者
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.49,0:05:32.83,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}并使大多数人受益\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and if it will benefit the greatest number.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:39.74,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}墨子的思想流传很广\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Mo Tze was extremely popular,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:42.07,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但他身后的数百年\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but a few hundred years after his death,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.11,0:05:45.04,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}秦始皇  第一位皇帝\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Qin Shi Huang, the first emperor,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.08,0:05:48.11,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}统一了中国  独揽大权\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and unifier of China, took power.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.15,0:05:50.71,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他将一片大陆变成了一个国家\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}He took a continent and turned it into a nation
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.75,0:05:54.15,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个现在依然受他影响的国度  中国\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that now bears his name... China.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.19,0:06:01.66,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们大多数人对他的了解大多数是\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Most of us know Emperor Qin for the army of 7,000
