Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.86,0:06:09.80,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在秦始皇的领导下\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In Emperor Qin's drive
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.83,0:06:12.44,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为了巩固辽阔的帝国\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to consolidate his far-flung empire,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.47,0:06:14.14,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他采取极端的手段\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}he took drastic measures
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.17,0:06:16.64,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为所有事物都建立了标准\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to standardize everything within it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.67,0:06:19.61,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}包括 铸造单一货币\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This included mandating a single coinage,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.64,0:06:22.18,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}统一度量衡\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}making uniform all weights and measures,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:26.02,chs&eng,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}车辆与道路的宽度  还有\N{\blur3}{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the widths of carts and roads, as well as the precise way
